Surf the rednet superhighway with "chat", the networked chat program for CraftOS! Host chatrooms and invite your friends! Requires a Wired or Wireless Modem on each computer.

ex:
"chat host forgecraft" will create a chatroom with the name "forgecraft"
"chat join forgecraft direwolf20" will connect to the chatroom with the name "forgecraft", using the username "direwolf20"